Lijepo što su i djevojcice
bile pozvane.

142
00:29:33,015 --> 00:29:34,653
Koliko znam o školi
za djecake...

143
00:29:34,815 --> 00:29:36,726
...djevojcicama je bilo
ljepše doma.

144
00:29:36,895 --> 00:29:40,092
- Jezivo.
- Korisno za novu knjigu.

145
00:29:41,455 --> 00:29:43,047
Necakinji sam procitao
Mocvaru...

146
00:29:43,215 --> 00:29:46,446
...i moram vam reci da je jezovita.

147
00:29:46,615 --> 00:29:49,175
Sve dobre djecje knjige su mracne.

148
00:29:49,335 --> 00:29:52,930
Braca Grimm, Ezop, Roald Dahl.

149
00:29:53,095 --> 00:29:55,768
"" Ring Around the Rosy""
je o umiranju od kuge.

150
00:29:55,935 --> 00:30:00,804
Strašna cudovišta u dubokoj,
mracnoj mocvari. Jezovito.

151
00:30:01,335 --> 00:30:02,973
Bajke i djecje pjesme...

152
00:30:03,135 --> 00:30:06,172
...djeluju na iskonski, podsvjesni
strah mladoga uma.

153
00:30:06,335 --> 00:30:09,088
Kažete da sva djeca vole
da ih se plaši?

154
00:30:09,255 --> 00:30:10,973
Vi niste?

155
00:30:11,615 --> 00:30:14,175
Znate li price o ovome mjestu?

156
00:30:14,335 --> 00:30:16,291
Kakve, jezovite?

157
00:30:16,775 --> 00:30:21,371
Škriputave daske, lupanje
vratima, fijuk vjetra...

158
00:30:21,895 --> 00:30:23,772
Vi pisci...

159
00:30:24,255 --> 00:30:25,404
Slušajte.

160
00:30:25,575 --> 00:30:28,453
Reci cu vam sve što znam
sutra za vecerom.

161
00:33:10,895 --> 00:33:13,045
Platz! Platz! Platz!

162
00:33:13,335 --> 00:33:15,610
Platz. Platz.

163
00:33:16,535 --> 00:33:19,333
- Obicno je miran.
- Ne bi se reklo.

164
00:33:20,775 --> 00:33:23,209
- Vi ste Geoffrey Hunt?
- Hunt.

165
00:33:23,375 --> 00:33:25,843
- Svi me zovu Hunt.
- Claire Holloway.

166
00:33:26,015 --> 00:33:29,371
Vec se jako dugo nije
tako naljutio, Claire.

167
00:33:29,535 --> 00:33:31,651
Samo je jedan razlog za to.

168
00:33:31,815 --> 00:33:34,170
Da? Koji?

169
00:33:37,815 --> 00:33:40,613
- Kad nanjuši duha.
- Što?

170
00:33:41,055 --> 00:33:45,526
Kao isparavanja s druge strane.

171
00:33:46,335 --> 00:33:47,893
Ne vjerujem u duhove.

172
00:33:49,815 --> 00:33:51,407
Niti ja.

173
00:33:52,215 --> 00:33:53,967
ldem za vama.

174
00:33:57,575 --> 00:33:58,803
Ovo mjesto?

175
00:33:58,975 --> 00:34:00,806
- Vec ste bili tu?
- Prije 3 godine.

176
00:34:00,975 --> 00:34:02,090
Kako se zvala?
Grace?

177
00:34:02,255 --> 00:34:03,449
- Mercy.
- Da.

178
00:34:03,615 --> 00:34:07,654
Vi ste savjetnik za paranormalno
koji ne vjeruje u duhove?

179
00:34:07,815 --> 00:34:09,487
Vjerujem u ljude.

180
00:34:09,655 --> 00:34:11,725
Ljudi su voda i energija.

181
00:34:11,895 --> 00:34:14,568
Voda se pretvara iz
leda u paru, maglu...

182
00:34:14,735 --> 00:34:18,887
...a i energija se može pretvarati,
zašto ne mogu ljudi?

183
00:34:19,615 --> 00:34:20,889
Što se dogodilo Mercy?

184
00:34:21,055 --> 00:34:24,650
Samo se malo prestrašila.
Buke. Ništa znacajno.

185
00:34:24,815 --> 00:34:26,806
Te energije mogu biti osobite.

186
00:34:26,975 --> 00:34:29,728
Mogu se otkriti jednoj
osobi, a drugoj ne.

187
00:34:29,895 --> 00:34:31,453
Zašto meni?

188
00:34:32,415 --> 00:34:34,371
To vi meni recite.

189
00:34:38,175 --> 00:34:40,086
Bio je ondje?

190
00:34:46,935 --> 00:34:48,926
Ulaz.

191
00:34:51,135 --> 00:34:52,727
Ulaz?

192
00:34:55,375 --> 00:34:57,127
Njihova pristupna tocka.

193
00:34:57,295 --> 00:35:00,253
Racunalo je druga.
To cu sada preskociti.

194
00:35:08,095 --> 00:35:10,006
Koliko je dugo ovo ovdje?

195
00:35:11,415 --> 00:35:13,167
Par dana. Zašto?

196
00:35:13,975 --> 00:35:15,931
S druge strane...

197
00:35:17,375 --> 00:35:23,769
...vrata mogu biti i simbolicna
i doslovna u isto vrijeme.

198
00:35:24,895 --> 00:35:26,613
Skidanjem...

199
00:35:28,575 --> 00:35:31,135
...se može nekoga
sprijeciti da prijede.

200
00:35:32,375 --> 00:35:36,084
Pa kad opet stavite vrata...

201
00:35:37,375 --> 00:35:38,808
Pozivate ih natrag.

202
00:35:51,175 --> 00:35:53,894
Definitivan porast
energije. Sigurno.

203
00:35:54,055 --> 00:35:56,523
- No zašto?
- Ljudi su cudni.

204
00:35:56,695 --> 00:35:59,687
A kad umru, postanu još cudniji.

205
00:36:00,055 --> 00:36:02,250
Pitanje je,
zašto je vama stalo?

206
00:36:03,615 --> 00:36:05,173
Jer sam vidjela...

207
00:36:05,335 --> 00:36:08,168
Vec sam vidjela tu
djevojcicu, ne samo tu.

208
00:36:08,335 --> 00:36:10,530
Znate li s cime se suocavate?

209
00:36:10,695 --> 00:36:14,051
To je drugi svijet.
Ne igraju po vašim pravilima.

210
00:36:14,415 --> 00:36:18,488
Prije sedam godina
izgubio sam suprugu i kcerku.

211
